Interface Delivery

DeliveryImpl
public interface Delivery
Delivery
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     Delivery delivery = Delivery.builder()
             .id("{id}")
             .createdAt("{createdAt}")
             .plusItems(itemsBuilder -> itemsBuilder)
             .plusParcels(parcelsBuilder -> parcelsBuilder)
             .build()
